item.title: Get involved
item.description: Help making Gatekeeper better! Gatekeeper is an open source project and developed collaboratively. Even if you're not a developer, you can get involved and make a difference. Community Chat Help other Gatekeeper users and developers by joining our communication chat and answering questions. Join the chat Development Contribute to Gatekeeper by fixing issues, improving functionality or implementing new features.
